videos.description: With the Seminoles running, Terance Mann throws up the lob to Dwayne Bacon who throws down the alley-oop to get the crowd in Tallahassee on its feet.
videos.headline: Alley-oops to Bacon are always a great idea

videos.description: Jarquez Smith blocks Steve Vasturia's floater
videos.headline: Jarquez Smith with the big block

videos.description: V.J. Beachem flies down the baseline for the monster dunk but Johnathan Isaac is there to put an end to that with a massive block resulting in a shot clock violation for Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Don't you dare try dunking when Isaac is lurking

videos.description: Jonathan Isaac gets the pass from  Xavier Rathan-Mayes and makes the lay up and the foul.
videos.headline: Jonathan Isaac gets the lay in and the foul

videos.description: J. Isaac made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by X. Rathan-Mayes.
videos.headline: Jonathan Isaac hits 3 to extend FSU lead in closing minutes
